genresAdvancedInfo.name: ethiopian hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A genre that blends traditional Ethiopian music with contemporary hip hop beats and lyrics. It often addresses social and political issues, as well as personal struggles and experiences. Ethiopian hip hop artists have gained recognition both locally and internationally for their innovative style and meaningful messages.
